<br>
For your big gun, look for a GE Man-Portable Laser, Steiner, Flashpoint, or Westinghouse Plasma Burner. These are all really slow, but they do massive damage. The idea is to put both guns on your hotkey bar so you can switch between them quickly. Use the big gun to quickly fire a burst or full-auto, then switch to your regular gun for the rest of the fight while the special recycles. It used to take forever to recycle, so I would save my GE for emergencies, but since the last patch I can burst with it once almost every fight.<br>
<br>
The best place to get armor is by camping the mission generator, or buying it from other players. You can probably use anything starting out, but later you'll need to stay away from stuff that has Int or Psy reqs. I have a ton of armor banked if anyone needs it, but it's mostly stuff in the mid-teens and higher. <br>
<br>
The most important thing about chosing armor is to stay color-coordinated at all costs. The Omni-Tek Fashion Police have their hands full chasing down cross-dressing Atrox, they don't need any more headaches. Please people, always remember: fashion is everything. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=644.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=644.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=644.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=644.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.threadControl?topicID=644.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=644.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=644.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub10.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacin